Brutas, You are correct. However, I used just one example to point out to Lukaria the arrogance that pervades most of her posts. Let me explain a little deeper and I will leave Lukaria out of the following.<br>
<br>
/rant filter off<br>
<br>
It is my experience that most evangelical Christians are utterly convinced that most peopled are doomed to hell and that *they* (and they alone!) have the answers to salvation from that hell. There are no real alternate paths to god for these losers. If you are not &quot;orthodox&quot; you will fry as sure as I am typing this out!<br>
<br>
Furthermore, these same Evangelical Christians like to parade around their beliefs under the guise of love. In reality it is simple pity on their parts. They pity all non-believers, since they haven't experienced &quot;the joy of the Lord&quot;. Like fucking Amyway salesmen they peddle their goods! Ever meet an Amway salesman who didn't love their product? Who didn't think the company was far superior to all others? When they knock at your door they bash your use of Tide detergent because they have the ultimate soap! Evangelical Christians like to do that. If you are an atheist you must be a sad wreck of a person. Hell, Muslims have no joy at all and Buddhists are just empty meditating shells of shit all because they haven't the grace of god and the love of Christ in their lives!<br>
<br>
So the Evangelical Christian, with Bible in one hand, and the &quot;knowledge of Truth&quot; (with a capital T!) in their brains embark upon the world to deliver all us puny empty hearted non-believers from what has to be a muther-fucking painful existence. Nevermind that the world turned for millions of years without Judeo-Christianity in it! Nope, these hounds for the lord have to sniff out the unsaved because they are so commanded by their master and we heathens just have to be delivered from our painful, sin filled, lives!<br>
<br>
So in walks the Christian to a game board who decides to &quot;lovingly&quot; point people to Christ. Fact of the matter is the Christian is just a fucking soap dealer who wants to sell her product! The Christian knows nobody on the game board from Adam and could really care a flying fuck about the denizens of the board as real people. NO! It is all about promotion of a certain view. A way to &quot;score points&quot; for the lord! Sure, they always come off with &quot;I truly want to share my joy of the Lord&quot;. Well fucking good for you! Go pet your dog or cat and tell them bible stories while your at it. Join a god damn seminary and become clergy, but know that most people don't want to buy your product! Most people use a different brand! In short, it is arrogant to think that anyway could give a rats ass enough about YOUR viewpoints on Christianity and life in general to &quot;convert&quot;, Evnagelical Christian!<br>
<br>
It is OK for Evangelicals to share their opinions. Just don't start to sell your fucking product to me when we &quot;chat&quot;! Evangelicals should share their experiences but not fucking solicit with them!<br>
<br>
/rant filter on<br>
<br>
I have a hell of a lot more I could say, but I will leave it here. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
